<div id='communityQuestionsWithAnswers'>
<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1153437-i-picked-this-book-up-at-a-little-free">I picked this book up at a Little Free Library in the Midwest. I read a bit of it, but . . . Who is the author to think he speaks for Christians, or that he even knows what being a Christian is? I tried to give the book a chance but I was put off by all the glib catch-phrases. The main character, which is obviously the author, talks like he speaks for God. &quot;God has brought you this far Laura; He will bring you . . &quot;</a>
</div>
