        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer953964359" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16096127127121795789">I finished this book a few days ago, and I just can&apos;t stop thinking about it. It&apos;s not a perfect book by any means, but it was perfect for me at this moment in my life. I&apos;m only bummed I waited so long to finally get around to reading it.</span>
  <span id="freeText16096127127121795789" style="display:none">I finished this book a few days ago, and I just can't stop thinking about it. It's not a perfect book by any means, but it was perfect for me at this moment in my life. I'm only bummed I waited so long to finally get around to reading it.</span>
